1049:Core/Src/mimic.c ****     /* Live Polling Strategy:
1050:Core/Src/mimic.c ****        1. Loop until 'length' bytes received OR 'timeout' expires.
1051:Core/Src/mimic.c ****        2. Read byte-by-byte with a short timeout to check for data.
1052:Core/Src/mimic.c ****        3. Echo received characters immediately ("Live Polling").
